trier wallpapers, en mettre un par defaut avec bg

git config --global user.name "your_username"
git config --global user.email "github@mail.com"
ssh-keygen -C "github@mail.com" -t ed25519
xsel -b < ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub
copy and past the key on the clipboard to github SSH settings

then:
ssh -T git@github.com
On each repo for github to push with ssh keys:
git remote set-url origin git@github.com:your-repository.git

seulement si 4k :
cat ~/.Xressources
Xft.dpi: 192
Xft.autohint: 0
Xft.lcdfilter: lcddefault
Xft.hintstyle: hintfull
Xft.hinting: 1
Xft.antialias: 1
Xft.rgba: rgb

Regler problemes de compatibilites avec ecrans 4k : Xressources, polybar, rofi
